James Oliver, 48, was left with a serious leg injury after being allegedly hit by a car driven by Linda Currier, 53 . 
  Police report that they found Oliver in the driveway of a home in Noblesboro, Maine, on Saturday night . 
  They said that Currier caught him allegedly trying to sexually assault a 12-year-old girl . 
  The pair argued inside the home and then Currier allegedly hit Oliver with the car . 
  He was taken to hospital and charged with attempted gross sexual assault . 
 